headline: S&P Dow Jones Indices Announces Change to the S&P/TSX Canadian Dividend Aristocrats Index
summary: S&P Dow Jones Indices announces the following index change to the S&P/TSX Canadian Dividend Aristocrats Index as a result of the monthly dividend review. Change will be effective prior to the open of trading on Monday, June 2, 2025.
